  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Ursa!</h2><br>You have been contracted by a mining company to finish setting up some positional beacons on the surface of the planet. You will be provided a standard issue anti-gravity gun to help navigate the difficult terrain of Ursa. Also be sure to watch out for any hidden collectibles along the way!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Open World (you can walk all the way around the world)<br></li><li>Competitive Leaderboards<br></li><li>Hidden Collectibles<br></li><li>Achievements</li></ul>",
